data.description: What a special spot! This 3 bedroom Farmhouse sits overlooking a pond that spills over a beautiful waterfall into a roaring brook that borders the nearly 1 acre lot. The abundant windows bring in the light and the view. The views can also be enjoyed from the huge deck and yard. Generous space for outdoor living and entertaining. Newer furnace and AC Unit. Open front porch. Water is navigable, and trout, bass and pickerel are caught regularly. All located in a quiet cul-de-sac just outside Chester village. A Bird Watchers Paradise & an Artist's Retreat.
